# AGENTS.md

## Project
Codex History Search

Local web GUI for browsing and searching Codex CLI session history.

## Stack
Node.js
Express
SQLite
React

## Rules
- Original Codex session logs are read-only
- Store custom metadata separately in SQLite
- Build MVP first
- Keep dependencies minimal

## Workflow
1. propose structure
2. propose schema
3. implement backend
4. implement frontend
5. connect resume
